title: Readout Of Phone Call Between Presidents Obama And Calderon | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




May 02, 2009

 



Readout Of Phone Call Between Presidents Obama And Calderon




THE WHITE HOUSE Office of the Press Secretary ____________________________________________________ For Immediate Release                       May 2, 2009    Readout of phone call between Presidents Obama and Calderon  Presidents Obama and Calderon spoke for 20 minutes this afternoon to share information about each country's efforts to limit the spread of the 2009 H1N1 flu strain and the importance of close U.S.-Mexican cooperation.   ###
